essors (required to ensure a healthy state of the blockchain network) is\neasier to achieve with the proposed incentive-compatible reward sharing\nmechanism than with other reward sharing mechanisms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Sep 2018 17:32:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Sep 2018 23:15:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-26"}
