AN). We are able to achieve quite good\nresults with very high average accuracy of 87.1% and as well a high ROC for ABS\nvs GCAN. For ABS vs HRHR, our model yields a high average accuracy of 86.22%.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Sep 2018 18:06:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-21"}
