ction to galaxy clustering measurements\nfor the complete 3 pass survey, and also after 1 pass, which is highly\nincomplete.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Sep 2018 18:07:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Jan 2019 15:40:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-16"}
